# get_irida_project
# get full details for a single IRIDA project
#
# NOTE: use get_irida_projects (no argument) to list all projects and their IDs
# get_irida_project returns full detail for a single project by ID. Takes a
# project ID argument, get_irida_projects does not
#
# example: get_irida_project [TAB once for project id] 105:Slush_Sub
